OL,3,CReward offered to catch law student's
OL,4,Ckiller 30 years on
OL,6,FA fresh appeal has been launched to
OL,7,Ffind the killer of a university
OL,8,Fstudent who was found dead in a river
OL,9,Fexactly three decades ago.
OL,11,FJanet Murgatroyd, 20, was discovered
OL,12,Fin the River Ribble, in Preston, on 16
OL,13,FJune 1996 but, despite a lengthy
OL,14,Fpolice investigation, her murder
OL,15,Fremains unsolved.
OL,17,FNow, independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,18,Fis offering a #20,000 reward for
OL,19,Finformation that finally brings her
OL,20,Fkiller to justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
