OL,3,CReward offered to catch law student's
OL,4,Ckiller 30 years on
OL,6,FThe University of Central Lancashire
OL,7,Fstudent, from Penwortham, had been out
OL,8,Fwith a friend on Saturday, 15 June,
OL,9,Fwhen she was attacked as she walked
OL,10,Fhome alone from Preston town centre.
OL,12,FThe pair were at the Adelphi pub
OL,13,Fbefore becoming separated. Janet left
OL,14,Fthe pub with a known man who she
OL,15,Fwalked down Fishergate with before
OL,16,Fthey parted company in the Church
OL,17,FStreet area.
OL,19,FCCTV later captured Janet walking
OL,20,Falone along Fishergate, heading
OL,21,Ftowards her home in Penwortham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781524080
OL,3,CReward offered to catch law student's
OL,4,Ckiller 30 years on
OL,6,FIt is known that Janet paused near
OL,7,FPreston Railway Station, where her
OL,8,Fpurse was stolen. She then continued
OL,9,Fdown Fishergate Hill towards
OL,10,FPenwortham Bridge.
OL,12,FAt some point after reaching the
OL,13,Fbridge, Janet was subjected to a
OL,14,Fviolent attack on Holme Road near to
OL,15,Fthe entrance of Priory Park, on the
OL,16,Fsouth side of the River Ribble.
OL,18,FShe sustained fatal head injuries and
OL,19,Fwas later found in the river by
OL,20,Fmembers of the public on the morning
OL,21,Fof Sunday, 16 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
