OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781524080
OL,3,CReward offered to catch law student's
OL,4,Ckiller 30 years on
OL,6,FDetectives believe the attack was
OL,7,Fsexually motivated. All of her
OL,8,Fclothing, with the exception of her
OL,9,Fjeans, was discovered left on the
OL,10,Friverbank.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination later
OL,13,Fconcluded that the cause of death was
OL,14,Fdrowning and head injuries.
OL,16,FIn October 2002, a 22-year-old man was
OL,17,Fcharged with manslaughter in
OL,18,Fconnection with Janet's death, but his
OL,19,Fconviction was later quashed at the
OL,20,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
