OL,3,CReward offered to catch law student's
OL,4,Ckiller 30 years on
OL,6,FDuthie added: "If you know something
OL,7,Fabout what happened to Janet that
OL,8,Fnight, however small it may seem,
OL,9,Fplease come forward. Your information
OL,10,Fcould make a real difference in
OL,11,Ffinally providing answers and justice."
